origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.analyze_interest_rate_sensitivity",
        "description": "分析房地产交易数据对利率变化的敏感性",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "transaction_data",
                "description": "房地产交易数据列表",
                "type": "LIST"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "sensitivity_analysis",
                "description": "利率敏感性分析结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.get_transaction_data",
        "description": "获取指定时间范围内的房地产交易数据",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "time_range",
                "description": "时间范围，格式为字符串",
                "type": "STRING"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "transaction_data",
                "description": "房地产交易数据"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.predict_future_impact",
        "description": "预测利率敏感性分析对未来房地产市场的影响",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "sensitivity_analysis",
                "description": "利率敏感性分析结果",
                "type": "DICT"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "future_impact_prediction",
                "description": "未来市场影响预测结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.provide_strategies",
        "description": "根据未来市场影响预测提供相应的房地产投资策略",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "future_impact_prediction",
                "description": "未来市场影响预测结果",
                "type": "DICT"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "strategies",
                "description": "房地产投资策略"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.calculate_property_value",
        "description": "根据市场数据计算特定房产的当前价值",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "market_data",
                "description": "市场数据",
                "type": "DICT"
            },
            {
                "name": "property_details",
                "description": "房产详细信息",
                "type": "DICT"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "property_value",
                "description": "房产当前价值"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.evaluate_investment_risk",
        "description": "评估特定房地产投资的风险水平",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "investment_details",
                "description": "投资详细信息",
                "type": "DICT"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_level",
                "description": "投资风险水平"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RealEstate.compare_market_trends",
        "description": "比较不同地区的房地产市场趋势",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "region_data",
                "description": "地区数据列表",
                "type": "LIST"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "trend_comparison",
                "description": "市场趋势比较结果"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
